' Demo1.dmc - Basic motor spin test
' Hardware: DMC-4143 -> DPRALTE-020B080 -> AKM21G
' Axis A, analog MCMD output (0-10V to drive)

SH C        ' Servo Here: enable axis C
SP 10000    ' Speed: 10000 counts/sec
AC 10000    ' Acceleration: 10000 counts/sec^2
DC 10000    ' Deceleration: 10000 counts/sec^2
PR 100000   ' Position Relative: move 100000 encoder counts
BG C        ' Begin motion on axis C
AM C        ' Wait until motion complete
MO C        ' Motor Off
EN          ' End program
